{"tid":491156,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔣麗芸指「全面開戰」：重光之時　李慧琼籲勿變戰場　","createTime":"2017-12-06T08:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T09:49:46.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0c6aaa1b5bd4fbe09ddecafc341c399c39ecdc94","tid":491156,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:49:12.000Z","msg":"立法會大會即將審議修改《議事規則》。民建聯立法會議員蔣麗芸於facebook上載圖片，大字寫上「全面開戰」，稱「修改議事規則之日，就是議會重光之時！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蔣麗芸指出，今個立法會年度至今未能通過一項法案，為避免濫用《議事規則》，影響立法會正常運作，修改《議事規則》事在必行 。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯主席李慧琼昨日形容今次是「硬仗」，估計泛民會用所有方法拖延，已有心理準備發生不同狀况，包括秩序混亂。她表示，民建聯會全程留在會議廳，謹守崗位，確保會議順利進行，呼籲議員不要把議會變成「戰場」，強調「議會是議事論事，講道理地方」。<br />\n<br />\n李慧琼今早晤傳媒時重申，建制派會「見招拆招」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171206/s00001/1512534876024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171206%2Fs00001%2F1512534876024&d=RrWYVrTiYs3SVwhRt8KSZGxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=f6d51626\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171206%2Fs00001%2F1512534876024&h=d9b52697\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171206/s00001/1512534876024</a>"},{"pid":"5b0c4307269e56a6e4fd0cc8843310e96130b709","tid":491156,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T09:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}